  <data key="d0">HippoCamp</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">HippoCamp is a benchmark for evaluating memory-augmented agents in realistic, device-resident personal file systems.&lt;SEP&gt;HippoCamp is an academic paper benchmarking contextual agents on personal computers.&lt;SEP&gt;HippoCamp refers to a controlled environment for evaluating contextual agents on personal computers.&lt;SEP&gt;HippoCamp is a benchmarking context for contextual agents on personal computers.&lt;SEP&gt;HippoCamp is a benchmarking context for contextual agents on personal computers.</data>
